    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In my opinion! I would leave the *.ps1 extension and rather use the '#requires -Version X' statement so I can at least provide some useful cross-platform scripting.  But, it only works in script file.  I would love this statement with the '-Version' to work in modules.\r\n\r\nAt the same time, we can always figured out other ways to make it work.\r\n\r\n:)",
